{"id": "b9e6eeb284b1ef903cc341bb58df6e583f73ab77c4d74a5cc7b970c5de4876f3", "item_id": "a4a6a36ec6:0", "text": "While Materials control the appearance of an object, patterns control the detail by varying the parameters of the material's Bxdf across a surface. This is similar to the way texture artists use textures to control the look of a material. RenderMan ships with a set of patterns that allow texturing, color correction, bumping, and various utility shading systems."}
{"id": "037afc208c73089dc1675c1276488d27737ebfbd9b307c07476dd26e6511e19c", "item_id": "a4a6a36ec6:1", "text": "The patterns can be divided into the following categories:"}
{"id": "2db13bea16181d66d343f0864eed10a4d0361dd1b79a49d969b78362ff49e297", "item_id": "a4a6a36ec6:2", "text": "Image Texture"}
