{"id": "71c327f075772db56c98ef88ca845f665795a8eea01c8daaf12239aca23b42b1", "item_id": "a4a6a36ec6:79", "text": "You do not need to be limited to the patterns that RenderMan provides.  If you follow the guidance in"}
{"id": "3a8cfe2b6fcd6e8a1fb51421bc72fc3e208a328425a8605c4e4790133fe8add8", "item_id": "a4a6a36ec6:81", "text": "you can build your own patterns.  XPU only runs OSL patterns, while RIS runs both C++ and OSL patterns."}
